XC_TEMPLE 




Amateur beautiful landscapes and of archeology, fascinated by the Incas you go on tour in their footsteps in the depths of a rainforest.
On your road, suddenly you stumble on a slippery rock and falling into a torrent.
You try to hang on a tree branch, a rock but the mainstream, you are taken straight to a waterfall.
Calling turning a blind eye not to die you make a fall a hundred meters.
You wake up bort knocked on the nape of a little water.
Seeking a hole in the rock a sword in hand, anger striking you in stone and it breaks.
On both curious and worried you would venture.
After two spans three stones you find In a wide clearing which seems trapped cliffs surrounding it.
You begin the climb up this one in search of your original route ...
Between beautiful scenery and secret passages, this map will be the lair of the most sophisticated climbers and fans of beautiful scenic!
